{
  "stem": "23626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I walked to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I walked to a park, a beautiful park.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they called it [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Plante ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And daily walk back and forth with my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And supposedly, from what I remember, I did very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was a good student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my mother kept my report card under her pillow when he-- she was dying, which we found later, because she was so proud of me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had straight A's, and I received an honorary tablecloth that was embroidered by the seventh graders.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was one that received that tablecloth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when my mother passed away, they found, in a hospital, under her pillow, my report card with the tablecloth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So it was rather important to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I followed my oldest sister's steps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was exceptionally bright, and I-- I just wanted to be like her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My oldest sister, Sydell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody would say, you are Sydell's sister?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are Sydell's sister?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, naturally I-- I had to follow her step.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was rather diligent, I would say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tried hard by-- by achieved what I was after.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I enjoyed school very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always wanted to be a nurse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I really felt that this was my [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] future, and helping people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, as it turned out to be, my daughter became a nurse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and later on, I-- I did follow a similar, similar profession that would be in the health field.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But naturally, at the time, [SIGHS] what happened afterwards, I-- [INAUDIBLE] never came through and I couldn't possibly go to school for nursing or whatever because time have changed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very similar.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just having fun.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
